Package com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registrars.repository

Class RepositoryEntityRegistrar

java.lang.Object
com.foreach.across.modules.entity.registrars.repository.RepositoryEntityRegistrar
All Implemented Interfaces:
EntityRegistrar, org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanClassLoaderAware
@Component public class RepositoryEntityRegistrar extends Object implements EntityRegistrar, org.springframework.beans.factory.BeanClassLoaderAware
Scans for Repository implementations and creates a default EntityConfiguration for them. Works for default Spring Data repositories that provide a RepositoryFactoryInformation bean and implement the RepositoryFactoryInformation.getPersistentEntity() fully.
Author:
Arne Vandamme
